manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: F145: Rockland Melbourne Hardside Expandable Spinner Wheel Luggage This carry on is made of polycarbonate. This material is extremely lightweight, durable, and protects the contents of your luggage. Multi-directional double spinner wheels rotate 360 degrees for easy maneuverability. This luggage allows you to pack more while avoiding the excess weight surcharges imposed by most airlines. 22"x13. 5"x9" (with wheels)

Features and Design Telescoping Handle The telescoping handle stows away conveniently and allows for easy maneuvering when extended. Expandable The upright expands an extra 2 inches in depth to maximize your packing capacity. Double Spinner Wheels Double spinner wheels allow for durable 360 degree maneuverability wherever your travels take you.

About Rockland Luggage Since its inception in 1998, Rockland by Fox Luggage has been proudly producing quality luggage and bags for the style savvy traveler. Recognized for its graphic and colorful designs, Rockland prides itself on creating products influenced by current trends in design and fashion. Our products turn heads in a crowd and stand out in the baggage carousel, making it easy for quick exits out the airport. Affordable and travel resistant, Rockland bags are an ideal companion for everything from quick trips to the gym to overnight getaways to extended vacations. Our selection includes: luggage sets (4 piece, 3 piece or 2 piece), hard cases, soft cases, carry ons, rolling backpacks, travel duffels, rolling duffels, cosmetic bags, and kids' backpacks. Over the years, a few Rockland products have been featured in film and television. Their colorful designs make them ideal for an eye catching visual element on screen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
Reviewed in the United States on April 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars CUTE and DOES THE TRICK!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for a trip to see my daughter at the last minute. It is REALLY cut, the color of Magenta/White made it super easy to identify when it was checked. I was unable to use it as a carry on because I simply could not lift it but it is compact and moves easily. Wheels glide across floors, handle goes up and down with no effort. I would highly recommend it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars It is ok
reviews.reviewText: It is not a heavy duty travel case. When just rolling it on all 4 wheels it is a little top heavy, But it is good for a over night bag, or going to grandparents home.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars exactly what i needed
reviews.reviewText: this roller case is exactly what i needed to replace my carry-on. it has ample amount of space, the construction is durable, its pretty and held up for flights plus road trip of the Pac NW.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Perfect carryon to hold vacation outfits for a week for one person. I purchased one of these for each of my family member. We fit our weeks worth of clothes in it for Universal studios FL and did not check any bags (1 carryon per person).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Broke, first time using this!
reviews.reviewText: Used for the first time this week traveling by air. The handle is broke, and won't go all the way down after extending it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for flying
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this for a 6 day trip to the desert. I wanted a carry-on, but I didn’t want to spend hundreds of dollars, as I don’t travel too often. I can’t believe how much I was able to fit in it! It worked out perfectly. I really like how well it rolled through the airport.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 3, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I so needed this
reviews.reviewText: I've needed new luggage for years now and it feels good to have this luggage. When I've traveled the last few years, I've seen people with luggage that looks like mine and that have wheels that maneuver in all directions and now I have one! They really do move around freely, can fit just enough things for me for a quick 3-4 day trip, and the outside is girly and futuristic. I love it!

reviews.reviewTitle: Great size and so easy to move around
reviews.reviewText: I loved travelling with this bag! My 6 year old daughter could easily move in it around the airport and it's a perfect size.Just remember to keep the extendable zipper closed if you want it to fit in the airport sizing box.
Llego antes de lo esperado. La maleta es muy bonita, igualita a la imagen. Actualizaré esta opinión cuando la use y vea que tal es de resistente.
